attributes.review:
I am a big fan of our Mr. President himself, Donald J. Trump ❤️😻. However this app is AWFUL. First things first, when I first opened the application, I was greeted by a very unflattering picture of a monster of some sort. It was orange and had papercut thin lips. This feels like a mockery of my beliefs and our country!  😡 Second of all, the overall format and idea of this app seems well made (of course cause I love Trump ❤️) but it isn’t. It’s a cheap way to praise a man like a god. NOT TO MENTION.....
“Spongebob hurry up with those orders!” 

“I’m sorry Squidward! I’m trying, I really” — he burped — “am.” His hands were everywhere. His silver spatula was whooshing through the air in record speed. Lettuce and Tomatoes were flying, pickles and cheese met the hamburger buns. Spongebob was about to add to the condiments when- “Ah, shrimp!” he exclaimed, grabbing his stomach and groaning. 

Squidward couldn’t help but whip around his head in shock. “Uh, Spongebob?” 
Spongebob couldn’t help but groan louder, pain pocking his sides. 
“Squidward,” he said in between pain filled groans, “I think..my water broke.” 

The squids eyes widened, joy and fear met his face. “I can’t believe it...it’s happening! It’s really happening!!” 

“Please, we need to go to the hospital,” the yellow square said, water dripping down his legs. 
Like lighting, Squidward snatched the sponge and ran to the hospital as fast as possible. It would only take minutes until he could see his new baby. 

Hours and hours passed, Squidwards brain was filled to the brim with worry and anxiety. “Did he make it?” he couldn’t help but ask himself as his tentacles paced the waiting room.
As if someone was reading his mind, one of the nurses came out of the emergency room and met her teary eyes with his worried ones.

“I-“ she said, stuttering, “I’m sorry Mr. Squidward...he didn’t make it.” 

His knees felt weak as he collapsed on the ground. The only one who was keeping him here in this sea, the only sponge he could ever love just left him. How could he live on? 

To be continued....

OVERALL, a very disappointing app. I do not recommend.
